cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper involves deep learning techniques for mapping roads from aerial imagery, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) categories. The paper also discusses data augmentation and convolution techniques, which are common in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper proposes a method to improve road extraction using crowdsourced GPS data, which can be relevant to robotics and automation (cs.RO) sub-category.
